Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.75,0:01:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(950,950)\pos(490,478)\fsp5\blur2}迷惑的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.97,0:01:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小子 不想受伤就退下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你们带走他的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:01:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是受伤这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小命可不保哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多重影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍法.五月雨血河
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我施展的可不是忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:02:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是杀人术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小李 你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 怎么没看到鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都平安无事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 不过没看到轰队长的踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纳命来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 放开我 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:03:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你回到同伴身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰 丸铁 你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们和小樱 浓眉他们也走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的任务是押送他去京城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是整条船都沉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那几个家伙居然追上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.77,0:06:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其让那些不忍带走他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如就地正法算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就地正法 什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正押送到京城也是死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私下行刑总比放跑他强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他能不能逃跑还不一定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的任务是押送这家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就让你立刻人头落地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里应该没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们好像迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们好像来到森林的最深处了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以通过月亮辨认方向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在回河边会有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们索性直接穿过森林去京城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务还是要执行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才不是说要把这家伙就地正法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是最坏的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.42,0:08:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道小樱他们现在怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭鸣人的实力 绝对不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赶快去找鸣人会合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:08:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小李
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有种奇怪的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小李
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们追
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许鸣人在他们手上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是向着月亮走的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月亮怎么跑到身后了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷惑的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦进入 就再也出不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是被押送的囚犯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没资格说话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这个迷惑的森林 你知道些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事 快说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不忍的老窝就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说我们在不忍的势力范围押送你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个森林最适合做为老窝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浓雾 突然吹起的狂风 强烈的磁场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都能打乱人们的方向感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次进来的人绝对无法出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们岂不是走不出森林了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你们来说是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不忍的成员 所以另当别论
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我带你们离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 你是不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就像你家的院子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 麻烦你带路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是傻瓜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以刚才那些不忍的身手来看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我承认这里就像你们家的院子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也相信不忍的老窝就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就更不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还搞不清楚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会假装穿越森林
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后带我们去他们的老窝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:11:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在事态紧急
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不死 我们就会死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种恶贯满盈的人 死有余辜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些伤是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我偷了不忍抢来的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被发现后 遭到他们严刑拷打
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那几个不忍并非救我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是想找回那些钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们拿到钱后 就会杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我会相信你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不忍的老窝就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些不忍就占有地利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们闯进不忍的院子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管丸铁是否背叛他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都可能被其他不忍攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我们现在的处境
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能相信他的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题 非常顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走这条小路他们很难发现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙真的值得信任吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就习惯这种蛇的毒性了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.98,0:14:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上当了 你们上当了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍法.土石翻身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上当的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是影分身和变身术的组合
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次轮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我怎么杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你少做梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙 打算趁机逃跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你出手相助 丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这架势 想动手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.54,0:19:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别以为骗得了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要跟着丸铁走 就能全身而退了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样 轰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.36,0:20:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的任务可是押送丸铁去京城啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人我无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家人以及弟弟 都被他杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸铁…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.69,0:22:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算丸铁是那群坏蛋的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你这样复仇又能得到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.10,0:22:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.48,0:22:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是押送丸铁去京城吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我觉得丸铁不像坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 如果你非要杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.31,0:22:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别怪我不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.26,0:23:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时我只能用武力阻止你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.08,0:23:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
